Package edu.utdallas.paged.mem.cache

Class Summary
CacheBase Abstract class that defines the base methods for any buffer
CacheObject A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of objects only
CachePredicate A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of predicates only
CacheSEfficient A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of subjects, predicates and objects as needed
CacheSubject A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of subjects only
CacheSubjectObject A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of subjects and objects only
CacheSubjectPredicateObject A specific implementation of the buffer based on caching the values of subjects, predicates and objects all at the same time
CacheSubjectRandomAlgorithm A specific implementation of the buffer based on randomly caching the values of subjects only
